HEADWORD: Tertium quid
<hw>Ter"ti*um quid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L.]</ety> <def>A third
somewhat; something mediating, or regarded as being, between two diverse
or incompatible substances, natures, or positions.</def>⟦br⟧
